<br>
                     <center><p><b>
                           <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                 <li>Does a high GDP relative to the CPI indicate a strong economy?</li>
                                 <br>
                                 <li>Is there a “sweet spot” in the middle?</li>
                                 <br>
                                 <li>How do countries that appear well off really line up?</li><br>
                           </ul>
         
                              </b></p></center>
