         <div class="jumbotron">
               <h3><center>A Snapshot of the Global Cost of Living</center></h3> 
               <h5><center>Using CPI to Track Living Costs</center></h5>
               <!-- Number of Countries and year include in jumbotron -->
                  <br>
             <p class="font-italic">
                  The economy of 159 countries for the year 2016 is visualized using three factors: <a style="color: lightseagreen" href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD" target="_blank">GDP</a>, <a style="color: lightseagreen" href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/FP.CPI.TOTL" target="_blank">CPI</a>, and the <a style="color: lightseagreen" href="https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/SP.POP.TOTL" target="_blank">country's population</a>. <br>
             </p>
         </div>

         <div class="row">
             <div class="col-2">
