               <p>Here we can see that higher levels of aid are generally given to companies scoring lower on the HDI. It appears that few countries scoring high on the HDI receive aid - only four received a low level and only one received a medium level.
                  <br>
                  <br>
                  There weren't many significant changes in 2016. The only notable change was that four more countries with medium development received a high level of aid.
